Click on the link below to access a set of use cases developed for Ontario eReferral FHIR Implementation Guide (IG) by the Canadian eReferral FHIR workstream 
to support implementers of systems that will use HL7 FHIR to support the electronic transfer of information when patients are referred from one healthare service 
provider to another in the province of Ontario.

https://simplifier.net/guide/ca-on-eReferral-r4-iguide-v0.10.1/usecases?version=current
